# UI and Styling Conventions

Best practices for building accessible and maintainable UI components using Mantine UI with the metallic blue color scheme and Framer Motion animations.

<rule>
name: ui_styling_conventions
description: Rules for UI development and styling standards with Mantine and Framer Motion
filters:
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: "\\.tsx$"

actions:
  - type: suggest
    message: |
      ## Framer Motion Animation Standards
      
      **IMPORTANT**: All animations MUST use Framer Motion. Do not use CSS transitions for complex animations.
      
      ### Setup
      ```tsx
      'use client';
      import { motion, useInView, AnimatePresence } from 'framer-motion';
      import { useRef } from 'react';
      
      // Create motion components from Mantine components
      const MotionBox = motion.create(Box);
      const MotionTitle = motion.create(Title);
      const MotionText = motion.create(Text);
      ```
      
      ### Standard Animation Patterns
      
      **Fade In Up (Primary entrance animation)**
      ```tsx
      const fadeInUp = {
        initial: { opacity: 0, y: 30 },
        animate: { opacity: 1, y: 0 },
      };
      
      <motion.div
        variants={fadeInUp}
        transition={{ duration: 0.5 }}
      >
        Content
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      **Stagger Children (For lists/grids)**
      ```tsx
      const staggerContainer = {
        animate: {
          transition: {
            staggerChildren: 0.1,
            delayChildren: 0.2,
          },
        },
      };
      
      <motion.div variants={staggerContainer} initial="initial" animate="animate">
        {items.map((item) => (
          <motion.div key={item.id} variants={fadeInUp}>
            {item.content}
          </motion.div>
        ))}
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      **Scroll-triggered animations (useInView)**
      ```tsx
      const ref = useRef(null);
      const isInView = useInView(ref, { once: true, margin: '-100px' });
      
      <motion.div
        ref={ref}
        initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 50 }}
        animate={isInView ? { opacity: 1, y: 0 } : { opacity: 0, y: 50 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
      >
        Content appears when scrolled into view
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      **Hover animations**
      ```tsx
      <motion.div
        whileHover={{ scale: 1.03, y: -5 }}
        whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}
        transition={{ type: 'spring', stiffness: 300 }}
      >
        Interactive element
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      **Continuous/Looping animations**
      ```tsx
      <motion.div
        animate={{ 
          y: [0, -10, 0],
          rotate: [0, 5, 0, -5, 0],
        }}
        transition={{ 
          duration: 4,
          repeat: Infinity,
          ease: 'easeInOut',
        }}
      >
        Floating element
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      ### Recommended Easing
      - **Standard**: `[0.22, 1, 0.36, 1]` (Custom cubic bezier - smooth deceleration)
      - **Spring**: `{ type: 'spring', stiffness: 300, damping: 20 }`
      - **Ease out**: `'easeOut'` for entrance animations
      - **Ease in out**: `'easeInOut'` for looping animations
      
      ### Timing Guidelines
      - **Fast interactions** (hover, tap): 0.2s
      - **Standard transitions**: 0.3-0.5s
      - **Entrance animations**: 0.5-0.7s
      - **Stagger delay**: 0.1s between items
      - **Scroll trigger delay**: 0.2-0.4s base delay
      
      ### AnimatePresence (For exit animations)
      ```tsx
      <AnimatePresence>
        {isVisible && (
          <motion.div
            initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
            animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
            exit={{ opacity: 0 }}
          >
            Conditionally rendered content
          </motion.div>
        )}
      </AnimatePresence>
      ```
      
      ## Metallic Blue Color System (Light Theme)
      
      | Purpose | Color | Hex Code |
      |---------|-------|----------|
      | Primary Metallic Blue | Main brand | `#1F4FD8` |
      | Electric Blue | Accent/hover | `#4DA3FF` |
      | Steel Blue | Secondary | `#3A6EA5` |
      | Deep Navy | Text primary | `#0A1A3F` |
      | Background White | Main BG | `#FFFFFF` |
      | Background Light | Section BG | `#F8F9FB` |
      | Text Muted | Secondary text | `#5A7099` |
      | Text Light | Tertiary text | `#8A9BB8` |
      
      ### Button Styling with Animation
      ```tsx
      <motion.div whileHover={{ scale: 1.03 }} whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}>
        <Button
          radius="xl"
          styles={{
            root: {
              background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #1F4FD8 0%, #4DA3FF 100%)',
              border: 'none',
              boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(31, 79, 216, 0.3)',
              transition: 'box-shadow 0.2s ease',
              '&:hover': {
                boxShadow: '0 6px 25px rgba(77, 163, 255, 0.4)',
              },
            },
          }}
        >
          Primary Action
        </Button>
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      ### Card Hover Animation
      ```tsx
      <motion.div
        initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
        animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
        whileHover={{ y: -8 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
      >
        <Box
          p="xl"
          style={{
            background: '#FFFFFF',
            borderRadius: 16,
            border: '1px solid rgba(10, 26, 63, 0.06)',
            boxShadow: '0 1px 3px rgba(10, 26, 63, 0.04)',
          }}
        >
          Card content
        </Box>
      </motion.div>
      ```
      
      ### Navigation Bar Animation
      ```tsx
      <motion.header
        initial={{ y: -100, opacity: 0 }}
        animate={{ y: 0, opacity: 1 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.6, ease: [0.22, 1, 0.36, 1] }}
      >
        <motion.div
          animate={{
            backgroundColor: isScrolled 
              ? 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95)' 
              : 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)',
          }}
          transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
          style={{
            backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
            borderRadius: 60,
            padding: '12px 24px',
          }}
        >
          Nav content
        </motion.div>
      </motion.header>
      ```
      
      ### File Organization
      ```
      src/
      ├── components/
      │   ├── Navigation.tsx    # Framer Motion header
      │   ├── Hero.tsx          # Staggered entrance animations
      │   ├── Services.tsx      # Card grid with scroll trigger
      │   ├── FeaturedWork.tsx  # Project cards with hover effects
      │   ├── Testimonials.tsx  # Quote with scale animation
      │   ├── About.tsx         # Team cards with stagger
      │   ├── CTA.tsx           # Interactive calendar
      │   ├── Footer.tsx        # Fade in on scroll
      │   └── Logo.tsx          # SVG logo component
      ├── theme/
      │   └── index.ts          # Mantine theme
      └── app/
          ├── layout.tsx        # MantineProvider
          ├── globals.css       # CSS utilities
          └── page.tsx          # Page composition
      ```

